name: Angel of Death
overview: A small-town policewoman is chasing a vicious serial killer; at stake is first a country girl's life, and then her own life.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Agnieszka is investigating a girl’s death in Opole: all evidence points to ritual murder. At the time, Piotr was teaching religious studies there.
